    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-09-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-09-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="385"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d385">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Armstrong</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-09-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 5, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Note just received from minister of state in reply to note of 18th last June
                    confirms agreement of Spanish minister at Washington. It says:</p>
                <p>In compliance with said agreement the Government has authorized Spanish minister
                    at Washington to pay on the date agreed upon, that is, the 15th instant, the sum
                    of 1,500,000 Spanish gold dollars, by drawing the equivalent sum in pounds
                    sterling, in drafts to your order and against the agent of the treasury of Spain
                    in London.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Armstrong</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
